author: Google
description:
Missed the Nano Banana Pro live launch? We’ve got you covered. 🍌✨

In this recap from our launch day live, you’ll hear everything you need to know about our newest model in under 10 minutes. 

- Multilingual Text Rendering: See how the model handles complex scripts (like Urdu) and design layouts with perfect accuracy.
- Reasoning with Gemini 3 Pro: Watch the model turn a YouTube video into a step-by-step "WikiHow" style guide.
- Visual & Spatial Design: From creating menus with "Bay Area prices" to annotating real-world castles with high spatial understanding.
- Creative Play: Generating cinematic wallpapers, consistent comic book characters, and even pixel art for arcade games.
- Search Integration: How we've merged the model's reasoning with real-time Search results for fresher, better answers.

Try Nano Banana Pro for free: http://gemini.google.com 
Build with the API: Get your keys in AI Studio: https://aistudio.google.com/

title: Launch Recap: Nano Banana Pro
